Process formatted water quality data

Source: R/process.R
process_wq.Rd

Process formatted water quality data

Usage

process_wq(df, start_date, end_date)

Arguments

df

Formatted dataframe returned from format_wq

start_date

Beginning of timeframe being evaluated (ex. first day of five-year assessment period).

end_date

End of timeframe being evaluated (ex. last day of five-year assessment period).

Value

Processed dataframe

Examples

process_wq(df_wq_formatted_example, "2015-07-01", "2020-06-30")
